      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节香瓜子葵花子促销</title>\n<style>\n    :root {\n        --color-red: #D62828;\n        --color-orange: #F77F00;\n        --color-light: #F4F4F5;\n        --color-dark: #003049;\n    }\n    body {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        background-color: var(--color-light);\n        color: var(--color-dark);\n    }\n    header {\n        background-color: var(--color-red);\n        color: white;\n        padding: 20px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    header h1 {\n        margin: 0;\n        font-size: 2em;\n    }\n    header p {\n        margin: 5px 0 0;\n        font-size: 1.1em;\n    }\n    section {\n        padding: 20px;\n        background-color: white;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #product-showcase img {\n        max-width: 100%;\n        height: auto;\n        display: block;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #pricing-info p {\n        margin: 5px 0;\n    }\n    #pricing-info p:first-child {\n        font-size: 1.4em;\n        color: var(--color-red);\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n    aside {\n        padding: 15px;\n        background-color: var(--color-orange);\n        color: white;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    aside div {\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #purchase-channel {\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n        align-items: center;\n    }\n    #purchase-channel input {\n        width: 60px;\n        padding: 5px;\n    }\n    #purchase-channel button {\n        padding: 8px 15px;\n        border: none;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        color: white;\n    }\n    #purchase-channel button:first-of-type {\n        background-color: var(--color-dark);\n    }\n    #purchase-channel button:last-of-type {\n        background-color: var(--color-red);\n    }\n    nav ul {\n        list-style: none;\n        padding: 0;\n        margin: 0;\n        display: flex;\n        gap: 10px;\n    }\n    nav ul li {\n        background-color: var(--color-light);\n        padding: 8px 15px;\n        border: 1px solid var(--color-dark);\n        cursor: pointer;\n    }\n    #shopping-cart {\n        background-color: white;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n    #shopping-cart div {\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    #shopping-cart button {\n        margin-right: 5px;\n        padding: 5px 10px;\n        border: none;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        background-color: var(--color-orange);\n        color: white;\n    }\n    footer {\n        background-color: var(--color-dark);\n        color: white;\n        padding: 20px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    footer p {\n        margin: 5px 0;\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<header id=\"header-top\">\n    <h1>春节香瓜子葵花子大促销</h1>\n    <p>欢聚佳节，香脆美味，欢迎选购！</p>\n</header>\n\n<section id=\"product-showcase\">\n    <img src=\"product.jpg\" alt=\"香瓜子葵花子高清图片\">\n    <p>精选优质瓜子，颗颗饱满香脆，净重500g，节日期间送礼佳品。</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"pricing-info\">\n    <p>现价：￥19.9 <del>原价：￥29.9</del></p>\n    <p>限时降价，立减10元，抓紧抢购！</p>\n</section>\n\n<aside id=\"promotion-elements\">\n    <div>倒计时：<span id=\"countdown\">02:15:48</span></div>\n    <div>库存紧张，仅剩20份！</div>\n    <div><button style=\"background:#003049; padding:5px 10px; border:none; color:white;\">领取优惠券</button></div>\n</aside>\n\n<section id=\"purchase-channel\">\n    <input type=\"number\" min=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n    <button>加入购物车</button>\n    <button>立即购买</button>\n</section>\n\n<nav id=\"category-navigation\">\n    <ul>\n        <li>坚果类</li>\n        <li>糖果类</li>\n        <li>饼干类</li>\n        <li>饮料类</li>\n    </ul>\n</nav>\n\n<section id=\"shopping-cart\">\n    <div>您的购物车：香瓜子葵花子 × 2</div>\n    <button>删除商品</button>\n    <button>修改数量</button>\n    <button>结算</button>\n</section>\n\n<footer id=\"footer\">\n    <p>© 2024 香瓜子葵花子商城 | 联系电话：400-888-8888</p>\n    <p><a href=\"#\" style=\"color: white;\">购买须知</a> | <a href=\"#\" style=\"color: white;\">帮助中心</a></p>\n</footer>\n</body>\n</html>"
